OL,3,CYoung muslims 'scared' to walk the
OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,FA group of young muslims say they feel
OL,7,F"scared" to walk the streets following
OL,8,Fthe riots across the UK, sparked by
OL,9,Fthe Southport stabbings.
OL,11,FMehran, Ruqayya, Sami and Haleema all
OL,12,Flive in the north of England, and
OL,13,Fbelieve more needs to be done to
OL,14,Ftackle racism.
OL,16,FWhen asked how Mehran was feeling
OL,17,Fafter the last couple of weeks, he
OL,18,Fsaid: "Quite scared, worried to leave
OL,19,Fhome, always second guessing whether
OL,20,Fwe should be in certain places at
OL,21,Fcertain times, and it's not nice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
