OL,3,CYoung muslims 'scared' to walk the
OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,F"It feels like we've gone back in time
OL,7,Fmany decades, and it's certainly not
OL,8,Fthe Greater Manchester or the UK that
OL,9,Fwe know and love."
OL,11,F"I think there is a huge need for us
OL,12,Fto come together now to think about
OL,13,Fhow we are reacting to this - not to
OL,14,Freact in the wrong way, not to fight
OL,15,Ffire with fire, not to add fuel to the
OL,16,Ffire - but to stay strong, and know
OL,17,Fthere is a path forward".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
