OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,FRuqayya is in her late teens, and has
OL,7,Flived in Bolton for her whole life.
OL,8,FShe said: "I'm 18 years of age now and
OL,9,Fit's a weird feeling for someone like
OL,10,Fme right now.
OL,12,F"I've grown up in this country, I was
OL,13,Fborn in Royal Bolton Hospital - my mum
OL,14,Fis a dental nurse, my dad's an avid
OL,15,Fmember of the community - this is all
OL,16,FI've known.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
