OL,3,CYoung muslims 'scared' to walk the
OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,F"So for me to feel fear coming here
OL,7,Fand speaking to people of colour, to
OL,8,Fsee people of colour in this
OL,9,Fconversation and for me to second
OL,10,Fguess whether I can go out the house -
OL,11,Fit's a very strange feeling to be
OL,12,Fhonest".
OL,14,FSami believes only those experiencing
OL,15,Fracism can fully understand what it
OL,16,Fmeans, and he continues to feel
OL,17,Felements of racism in the UK.
OL,19,FHe said: "Being from an asylum-seeking
OL,20,Fbackground, I feel like my community
OL,21,Fare specifically targeted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
