OL,3,CYoung muslims 'scared' to walk the
OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,F"On one side I feel like my community
OL,7,Fis Manchester and I've been Mancunian
OL,8,Fmost of my life, and I believe myself
OL,9,Fto be Mancunian, but this puts that
OL,10,Fentire sense of belonging in jeopardy.
OL,12,F"On the other side, I can also see
OL,13,Fthat the austerity that the previous
OL,14,Fgovernment has put people through,
OL,15,Fpeople feel neglected, they don't feel
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
