OL,3,CYoung muslims 'scared' to walk the
OL,4,Cstreets after riots
OL,6,F"And I sympathise with the fact that
OL,7,Fmost of the people who are in these
OL,8,Friots - they are not racist - they
OL,9,Fjust feel like they've not been heard
OL,10,F- and they just want somewhere to put
OL,11,Ftheir anger and frustration in and
OL,12,Fit's just been channeled through this
OL,13,Fway."
OL,15,FHe said: "I feel like racism is
OL,16,Fsomething you can only experience, you
OL,17,Fcan never truly understand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
